annotationA: Ribosomal RNA processing protein 1 homolog; May be involved in the generation of 28S rRNA
annotationB: Nopp140, isoform E; Nopp140 is a nucleolar and Cajal body protein. It is predicted to function as a chaperone in the assembly of small nucleolar ribonucleoprotein particles within Cajal bodies, their transit to nucleoli, and their association with pre-ribosomal RNA within nucleolar dense fibrillar regions
